{"tid":525024,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"物理題，究竟太空儀器粒CPU靠咩散熱？","createTime":"2018-01-10T08:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T16:08:15.000Z","uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68e8a87eb28291e1f785e08f6f32b12bb7c96d89","tid":525024,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"假設一粒CPU，係地球全速運行有90度<br />\n<br />\n上到太空（真空環境）冇粒子比佢做風冷<br />\n會唔會好似真空保溫樽咁，散熱效率超慢？"},{"pid":"fa1a6ef6cc9c79628921aede17393b9094844f4b","tid":525024,"uid":2772,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"radiation"},{"pid":"6726cfa661fabaed4ad60b14670effbb0f175550","tid":525024,"uid":2772,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"照你咁講<br />\n就算太陽哂到仆街都好<br />\n都冇粒子俾佢帶D熱力黎地球<br />\n<br />\n點解會熱"},{"pid":"6a63e4639cb0d91b085835f5963314b355b8fcee","tid":525024,"uid":135986,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"fa1a6ef6cc9c79628921aede17393b9094844f4b","tid":525024,"uid":2772,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"radiation"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"太空好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfac02d73460395dfc56ec23c84c3bd7b210fea7","tid":525024,"uid":149212,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"其實空氣粒子先係散唔到熱既主因(poor heat conductor)<br />\n上到太空一黎低溫, 二黎咩都無<br />\n散熱會好快"},{"pid":"38b43d57b71eab02d242a51cacc4a80480a738a6","tid":525024,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"其實我Google左答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n太空CPU好似設計到好難過熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過真係好奇，d間諜衛星影要不停處理咁多高清相<br />\nd CPU會點設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5